/* =====================================================================
   Rhea Code Compiler — exercise bank  (100+ per section)
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------
   Add exercises by pushing objects into RHEA_EXERCISES.python/.sql/.powerbi.
     id       unique stable string (used for progress)
     level    "beg" | "int" | "adv"
     title    sidebar label
     prompt   HTML instructions
     starter  editor pre-fill
     solution reference answer (shown under "Show solution")
     check    grading:
       Python -> { stdout:"..." }  and/or  { tests:"python asserts" }
       SQL/PBI -> { sql:"reference query", ordered:true|false }

   SQL + Power BI share one seeded SQLite DB (RHEA_DB_SEED). DAX exercises
   are graded by an equivalent SQL query ("DAX over SQLite" simulation).
   All Python solutions+tests and all SQL/DAX reference queries are
   verified to run/pass (see verify scripts in repo history).
   ===================================================================== */

